name: BIG FAT SANDWICH

reviews.review_text: Phenomenal once in a lifetime experience. We had breakfast. Their beverages were international. We had iced mocha, Vietnamese coconut coffee and iced latte. Everything was so good. For mains we had pesto pizza, pork sandwich, pork burger and a big fat platter. Everything swept us away with a lot of deliciousness. Fantastic. Reduced one star only for pricing. But absolutely worth it.

My wife and I visited Big Fat Sandwich for an early dinner and had a wonderful experience. We ordered the Aglio Olio Spaghetti and Barbecue Chicken Wings, both of which were delicious and served in generous portions. The flavors were spot on, and the food quality exceeded our expectations.

The service was excellent – the waiter was friendly and attentive, ensuring we had a comfortable dining experience. The restaurant offers good parking space, and the ambience was cozy and inviting, making it a perfect spot for a relaxed evening. The prices were reasonable, especially considering the quantity and quality of the food.

Although we found the locals in Goa not very friendly, restaurants like Big Fat Sandwich definitely make up for it. Highly recommend this place for a satisfying meal and great service!

We visited Big Fat Sandwich in Goa, during our trip in November, 2024 and had a really enjoyable experience. The atmosphere is cozy and welcoming, making it a perfect place to relax with friends or family. I ordered Grandma's Special Chicken Sandwich (a fried chicken sandwich), a classic Margherita pizza with onions, and a cappuccino. The sandwich was fantastic, featuring crispy fried chicken and a wonderful mix of flavors. The Margherita pizza was also delicious, and the addition of onions gave it a nice twist that I appreciated. The cappuccino was well-prepared and paired nicely with the meal. The service was friendly and efficient, and the prices were fair for the quality of food provided. However, the place can get quite busy, so be ready for a bit of a wait during peak times. Overall, Big Fat Sandwich is a great option if you're looking for a satisfying meal in Goa. I’ll definitely return to try more items from their menu!

They have car parking in front of the restaurant and a guy to help you park.

description:
### A Culinary Adventure at Big Fat Sandwich: Anjuna’s Hidden Gem

Nestled in the lively locale of Anjuna, **Big Fat Sandwich** has carved out a sweet spot in the hearts of locals and tourists alike, boasting an impressive **4.3 rating from 774 reviews**. Renowned for hearty offerings such as **pizza** (44 mentions), **sandwiches** (an 8-frequency highlight), and delectable **pork dishes**—the restaurant has established itself as a hotspot for those seeking flavorful and filling meals.

#### Ambiance & Design

Stepping into Big Fat Sandwich, guests are greeted by a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The décor blends rustic charm with a contemporary edge, creating a welcoming environment perfect for casual dining. Warm lighting bathes the space, accentuating its vibrant colors and eclectic decor, making it a visual feast that complements the culinary delights on offer. The intimacy of the setting fosters a relaxed vibe, enhanced by soft background music, ensuring a pleasant dining experience whether you're with loved ones or fellow travelers. 

![Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmUqS9lxjHU1Ta-SMZgsikFC4Mg3bAt-GxXMzyyTLQX3XrjRlB6ol-JQhLqL2AHPdMJ_OX-6F4Fcx5jU20ZlhMJzgIQzXbx5oAo87RjkB9V5hzbJoVSMKF9HC6ZLikblSwcYsU=w375-h281-p)

#### Menu & Culinary Experience

The menu at Big Fat Sandwich is a testament to its creativity and commitment to quality. Signature dishes have gained significant praise from patrons, with items like the **Grandma's Special Chicken Sandwich** and **Margherita Pizza** standing out for their generous portions and robust flavors. A standout aspect is the **pesto pizza**, which evokes rave reviews for its perfect balance of ingredients—an excellent representation of the restaurant's culinary prowess.

Picture diners feasting on a **pork sandwich**, its succulent meat bursting with flavor or savoring a **big fat platter** that perfectly showcases the restaurant’s commitment to variety and quantity, but don’t just take my word for it; the images captured by customers highlight these mouthwatering dishes that leave a lasting impression:

![Food Presentation](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnhpkDI34KInSkQqW4sAWqDKHtK84lgRo_PNINckvIQ37xNbRvWzt0DvoI8t-mvk6wXDa8ybYi_MtTka0gbb4SrA0n2MCAIGW90zlJ0v2qfI9Abe4kr9umWsXVCG9SZsOMvrCg=w375-h281-p)

With a well-curated drink menu that includes international options like **iced mochas** and **Vietnamese coconut coffee**, the beverage experience rounds out a delectable culinary journey. Additionally, dietary accommodations are acknowledged, with sufficient vegetarian options catering to diverse food preferences.

#### Customer Experience & Service

One of the hallmarks of Big Fat Sandwich is its attentive and friendly service, often reflected in customer reviews. Guests highlight the staff's warmth, with many describing their experiences as engaging and accommodating. Reviews note that the waitstaff goes above and beyond, ensuring that your dining experience is nothing short of comfortable. 

The restaurant offers convenient parking, which, combined with its welcoming atmosphere, makes it an ideal choice for a casual meal. While it can get busy during peak hours, patrons praise the seamless operation and the commitment of the staff to managing the flow, resulting in a solidly positive dining experience.

#### Popularity & Reviews

Big Fat Sandwich is not just a local favorite; it has generated a buzz online, with social media showcasing mouthwatering dishes that tempt food enthusiasts to visit. Customers laud the generous portion sizes and fair pricing, often stating that the value received makes this spot a must-visit. Critics and casual diners alike echo sentiments of satisfaction, reinforcing the restaurant's reputation as a go-to for satisfying meals in Goa.

#### Conclusion

With its inviting ambiance, impressive menu, and stellar service, Big Fat Sandwich stands out as a culinary highlight in Anjuna. Whether you’re leaning towards indulging in a hearty **sandwich** or creative **pizza**, this establishment promises to deliver a memorable dining experience that balances flavor, generosity, and warmth. From the delightful presentation of dishes to the friendly smiles of the staff, Big Fat Sandwich is a quintessential stop for anyone looking to enjoy the vibrant gastronomic scene of Goa.
